@TMSApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5229

### 1. GET All Enrollments (Should yield empty array initially)
GET {{TMSApi_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. POST Create New Enrollment (Should return 201 Created with Location Header)
POST {{TMSApi_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S-001",
  "courseCode": "CS-101"
}

###

### 3. GET Specific Enrollment by ID (Replace with the 8-char ID returned from Step 2)
GET {{TMSApi_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments/YOUR_RECORD_ID
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. DELETE Existing Enrollment
DELETE {{TMSApi_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments/YOUR_RECORD_ID

###

### 5. GET Deleted Enrollment Again (Should return uniform 404 Not Found JSON)
GET {{TMSApi_HostAddress}}/api/enrollments/YOUR_RECORD_ID
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. GET Trigger ProblemDetails Error (Should output clean JSON, no HTML)
GET {{TMSApi_HostAddress}}/api/error
Accept: application/json